like you were.

40:27.120 --> 40:29.731
But you weren't.

40:33.518 --> 40:35.084
How you doing?

40:35.128 --> 40:37.435
Good.

40:43.789 --> 40:46.052
I said, "How you doing?"
like that

40:46.095 --> 40:50.012
because your parents died
days ago.

40:54.103 --> 40:55.540
Yeah.

40:55.583 --> 40:58.107
You said, "Good."

40:58.151 --> 41:00.414
Okay.

41:00.458 --> 41:04.549
Sort of like...

41:04.592 --> 41:06.942
Sort of like what?

41:06.986 --> 41:10.337
Sort of like
they didn't.

41:15.211 --> 41:17.039
Where were you?

41:18.911 --> 41:20.739
And who's in the barn?

41:24.569 --> 41:27.093
Hay.

41:27.136 --> 41:29.356
Hey, what?

41:29.399 --> 41:30.531
Hay is in the barn.

41:30.575 --> 41:32.577
You asked
what was in the barn.

41:32.620 --> 41:35.841
I asked you
who was in the barn.

41:35.884 --> 41:37.233
Oh.

41:37.277 --> 41:39.888
I saw a human head
pass that slat.

41:39.932 --> 41:41.368
Hay doesn't walk,
Paul.

41:41.411 --> 41:44.066
They walked right on by.

41:44.110 --> 41:48.593
I was just in there alone,
so...nobody.

41:48.636 --> 41:50.072
[ Breathes deeply ]

41:50.116 --> 41:52.031
[ Sighs ]

41:55.469 --> 41:59.299
