if I can go in that barn.

41:59.342 --> 42:01.562
And you're gonna say
yes or no.

42:01.606 --> 42:03.390
And if you say yes,

42:03.433 --> 42:04.957
then I'm gonna walk
into that barn,

42:05.000 --> 42:06.349
and if there's
no one in there,

42:06.393 --> 42:08.569
in the manner you just
explained to me,

42:08.613 --> 42:10.832
well, good for you.

42:10.876 --> 42:12.878
But if you say no,

42:12.921 --> 42:16.272
I'm gonna regard that
as a fucked-up thing,

42:16.316 --> 42:21.669
another fucked-up thing,
a seriously fucked-up thing

42:21.713 --> 42:25.238
among the growing number
of really fucked-up things

42:25.281 --> 42:27.196
in your orbit, bud.

42:27.240 --> 42:31.070
And rather than go away,
I'm gonna bear down.

42:31.113 --> 42:36.075
And that'll get awfully fucking
ugly for you, kid.

42:39.252 --> 42:44.039
A girl is dead,
you dumb motherfucker.

42:44.083 --> 42:48.566
Now walk me over
to that barn.

42:51.743 --> 42:54.789
[ Birds cawing ]

43:18.770 --> 43:20.162
Let's go to
the barbershop.

43:20.206 --> 43:21.860
I'm eager to hear
where you've been.

43:28.257 --> 43:30.085
Paul: [ Whispering ]
We're hunkered.

43:39.138 --> 43:40.748
[ Railroad crossing dinging ]

43:40.792 --> 43:42.054
We've got an hour.

43:42.097 --> 43:44.447
Want to explore
or something?

43:59.245 --> 44:01.029
Shouldn't we get back?

44:01.073 --> 44:03.292
For the bus?

44:03.336 --> 44:05.512
We've got
a little time.

44:10.473 --> 44:12.824
[ Leaves crunching ]

44:14.608 --> 44:16.654
Check it out.

44:31.756 --> 44:34.628
[ Door opens ]

44:40.112 --> 44:41.722
What is this place?

44:41.766 --> 44:43.332
Paul: It's mine.

44:43.376 --> 44:46.814
It's called The Little Cabin
That is Totally Not Scary

44:46.858 --> 44:50.035
But Rather is Oh So Filled
with Fun and Safety

44:50.078 --> 44:52.602
And You Can Stay Here
for Three Whole Days

44:52.646 --> 44:55.388
and be So Safe
and Very Merry.

44:55.431 --> 44:56.650
[ Chuckles ]

44:56.694 --> 44:59.435
All is not
what it seems.

44:59.479 --> 45:01.611
There's no bathroom
in the magic cabin.

45:01.655 --> 45:06.007
Or certainly you have to go
through magic portals

45:06.051 --> 45:11.273
