45:26.898 --> 45:29.117
My Houdini cuffs.[ Chuckles ]

45:29.161 --> 45:30.466
Cool, bro.

45:30.510 --> 45:32.251
I got them for you,
these cool boys.

45:32.294 --> 45:33.643
[ Handcuffs clicking ]

45:33.687 --> 45:35.558
I thought I was too young
for these cool boys.

45:35.602 --> 45:37.735
You are --
for the water part.

