start practicing here,

45:51.183 --> 45:53.185
see if you can get out.

45:56.971 --> 45:59.931
Are you sure
these are Houdini cuffs?

45:59.974 --> 46:02.020
You're supposed to be able to
twist and pop them,

46:02.063 --> 46:03.586
pop them on open.

46:03.630 --> 46:06.415
I already learned the twist,
but these aren't popping.

46:06.459 --> 46:09.854
Do they only work
in the water?

46:09.897 --> 46:11.986
Keep trying.

46:22.867 --> 46:24.999
Paul?

46:25.043 --> 46:28.089
