48:57.673 --> 49:00.981
into earth...

49:01.025 --> 49:03.810
and then into mist...

49:03.853 --> 49:07.031
then into rain.

49:07.074 --> 49:12.340
And they will lift
and fall this way.

49:12.384 --> 49:19.565
And they'll lift
and fall this way five-ever.

49:22.568 --> 49:24.962
So, what do you think?

49:25.005 --> 49:27.094
New Leaf?

49:27.138 --> 49:29.314
About what?

49:29.357 --> 49:31.272
About, you know, your --

49:31.316 --> 49:35.755
your vehicle hauler
parent conundrum.

49:35.798 --> 49:38.714
If you're asking
what I'm thinking,

49:38.758 --> 49:46.070
I'm thinking I don't know
a fucking thing about you, man.

49:49.899 --> 49:52.119
My father taught me to be aware
of my surroundings,

49:52.163 --> 49:54.295
and you're all
surrounding me.

49:54.339 --> 49:56.384
And I don't know shit.

49:56.428 --> 49:59.561
I just know there's some
fucking money somewhere

49:59.605 --> 50:05.089
and some fucked-up
old, loose guy somewhere.

50:05.132 --> 50:08.918
And I'm very uneasy
about the desecration

50:08.962 --> 50:12.531
of the only thing
that is dear to me.

50:14.098 --> 50:18.580
Very uneasy...
certified muff diver.

50:21.279 --> 50:22.454
Ahh.

50:22.497 --> 50:24.238
[ Mug thuds ]

50:24.282 --> 50:27.807
How do you know
I'm a certified muff diver?

50:27.850 --> 50:31.115
Picture of you.

50:33.726 --> 50:35.728
Picture of me where?

51:20.164 --> 51:22.035
[ Monitor beeps ]

51:25.734 --> 51:29.129
You making progress on
your hundred sad phone calls?

51:29.173 --> 51:31.523
Nearly done.

51:31.566 --> 51:35.657
You'll be having a memorial
service soon, I imagine?

51:35.701 --> 51:37.877
At Our Lady?

51:37.920 --> 51:40.140
Just waiting for the --

51:40.184 --> 51:43.361
you know, my parents...

51:43.404 --> 51:45.972
to arrive from Mexico.

51:46.015 --> 51:49.454
Your Uncle Dave is eager
to help with that.

51:51.934 --> 51:57.026
I'm obligated, Paul, to know
about your whereabouts.

51:57.070 --> 51:59.464
Just because you didn't have
that gizmo on your leg

51:59.507 --> 52:01.205
