you're off the hook.

52:01.248 --> 52:04.338
So, I'm asking.

52:04.382 --> 52:06.993
Where the fuck
have you been?

52:10.344 --> 52:12.259
And if you tell me
that you can't tell me,

52:12.303 --> 52:14.131
I'm gonna tell you
that you're gonna.

52:14.174 --> 52:18.135
You're gonna tell me soon,
some way.

52:20.224 --> 52:21.660
You got bit
by a rattlesnake.

52:21.703 --> 52:23.531
This we know.

52:23.575 --> 52:26.360
And this is unusual.
Doesn't happen every day.

52:26.404 --> 52:30.059
So, describe to me
the day this happened to you,

52:30.103 --> 52:32.801
what went on before,
what went on after,

52:32.845 --> 52:36.196
the day you left the hospital
without the monitor on your leg.

52:36.240 --> 52:39.373
Now.

52:41.941 --> 52:44.639
I need to know my surroundings,
I'm saying,

52:44.683 --> 52:48.208
if I'm gonna allow the smashing
of my elderly father, Kevin,

52:48.252 --> 52:52.212
and my mother, Denise,
by a fucking big truck, Paul.

52:52.256 --> 52:55.172
Let's hear it.

52:57.957 --> 52:59.785
Hear what?

52:59.828 --> 53:01.917
What the fuck?

53:01.961 --> 53:05.007
What the fuck what?

53:05.051 --> 53:11.231
What the fuck is going on,
the whole thing.

53:17.977 --> 53:20.675
There was a little girl.

53:22.895 --> 53:26.203
The only person I ever met
who loved magic as much as me.

53:26.246 --> 53:27.421
[ Grunts ]

53:27.465 --> 53:30.685
She was a magic kid, too,
you know?

53:30.729 --> 53:32.687
Magic how?

53:32.731 --> 53:35.951
In all the ways.

53:38.737 --> 53:41.261
And something terrible
happened to her...

53:43.437 --> 53:44.960
'cause of me.

53:45.004 --> 53:47.136
♪♪

53:47.180 --> 53:49.095
Something terrible
happened to her

53:49.138 --> 53:53.360
that wouldn't have
if I never lived.

53:53.404 --> 53:55.449
♪♪

53:55.493 --> 53:59.540
And I'm gonna think about this
five-ever...

53:59.584 --> 54:02.500
when I'm me...

54:02.543 --> 54:06.678
when I'm down
under the earth...

54:06.721 --> 54:10.334
when I'm water.

54:10.377 --> 54:12.988
♪♪

54:13.032 --> 54:15.600
The Magic Kid.

54:15.643 --> 54:17.428
♪♪

54:17.471 --> 54:19.865
I'm gonna think of her
five-ever.

54:19.908 --> 54:26.567
♪♪

